{
  "stem": "21437.8",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I-- I suddenly felt-- maybe not suddenly, maybe it evolved-- then a day was a very long time.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "After the war, a day was-- was endless.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I felt, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I think that-- that bitterness and hate doesn't mix.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And if, perhaps, I don't know if I consciously, but I knew that-- I knew that I was going to meet a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I didn't really want to talk about it that much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't want to go, and look what has happened to me, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because it had happened-- it happened to the others, as well.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But I told, like always, I'm going to search for something, which is-- which will allow me to put-- to-- to acknowledge who I am.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because at that stage, I knew that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, it was shoved down my throat often enough, you know?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So where other kids, when they were growing up, it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You know, with me, OK, it worked-- it worked in-- in-- in an assisting way in the long run.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I think that, again, this is when it came into focus, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that I know who I am.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you didn't have the role-- you know, now, about the role models.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And one thing we didn't have, one thing we were not aware of, that we had a-- had a poor self-image.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So I really didn't-- I never sort of had a poor self-image, you know?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Because the others didn't have either.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "When you live at such close proximity, even after the liberation, wherever it was, you went-- I went-- I decided to go back to Poland.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There were hundreds, swarming, literally, you know, of survivors.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They already recovered a bit.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
